== 领土争端 ==
2015年6月2日，马来西亚首相署部长[[沙希淡卡欣|沙希旦卡欣]]指责一艘中国海警船已经在巴丁宜阿里浅滩锚泊了大约两年时间。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theborneopost.com/2015/06/03/china-coast-guard-vessel-found-at-luconia-shoals/|title=China Coast Guard vessel found at Luconia Shoals|work=Borneo Post|date=2015-06-13|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501125820/http://www.theborneopost.com/2015/06/03/china-coast-guard-vessel-found-at-luconia-shoals/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://thediplomat.com/2015/06/malaysia-responds-to-chinas-south-china-sea-intrusion/|title=Malaysia Responds to China’s South China Sea Intrusion|work=The Diplomat|date=2015-06-09|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313233859/https://thediplomat.com/2015/06/malaysia-responds-to-chinas-south-china-sea-intrusion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年3月24日，马来西亚政府发现约100艘中国船只入侵巴丁宜阿里浅滩海域。沙希旦表示已下令[[马来西亚海事执法局|马来西亚海事执法局]]部署三艘船只对该地区进行监测，而马来西亚皇家海军也在那里拥有资产。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/03/134965/more-100-china-vessels-spotted-malaysian-waters|title=More than 100 China vessels spotted in Malaysian waters|work=New Straits Times|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108163223/https://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/03/134965/more-100-china-vessels-spotted-malaysian-waters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://thediplomat.com/2016/03/100-china-ships-encroaching-malaysias-waters-minister/|title=Around 100 China Ships Encroaching Malaysia’s Waters: Minister|date=2016-03-25|work=The Diplomat|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108223545/https://thediplomat.com/2016/03/100-china-ships-encroaching-malaysias-waters-minister/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年7月14日，马来西亚总稽查署公布《2018年第三系列总稽查司报告》，报告显示中国军警在2016年至2019年期间曾入侵马来西亚水域多达89次，主要集中在巴丁宜阿里浅滩区域，其中有72次是[[中国人民武装警察部队海警总队|中国海岸警卫队]]所为，其余17次则是[[中国人民解放军海军|中国人民解放军海军]]。马来西亚外交部曾在2017年针对中国军警入侵海域而向中国提出第一份外交照会，随后也在2018至2019年期间5次向中国递交了[[外交照會|外交照会]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/07/14/china-intruded-into-msian-waters-89-times-in-last-three-years-says-audit-report|title=China intruded into M’sian waters 89 times in last three years, says audit report|work=The Star|date=2020-07-14|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404005311/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/07/14/china-intruded-into-msian-waters-89-times-in-last-three-years-says-audit-report|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2020/07/14/351813|title=【稽查报告】89次！中国军警船闯东马海域|work=东方Online|date=2020-07-14|accessdate=2021-06-02|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312033922/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2020/07/14/351813|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=◤审计报告◢ 3年89次！ 中国军警船侵东马海域【內附音頻】中國報|url=https://www.chinapress.com.my/20200714/%e2%97%a42018%e5%b9%b4%e6%80%bb%e5%ae%a1%e8%ae%a1%e5%8f%b8%e6%8a%a5%e5%91%8a%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%973%e2%97%a23%e5%b9%b489%e6%ac%a1%ef%bc%81-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%86%9b%e8%ad%a6%e8%88%b9-%e4%be%b5%e4%b8%9c/|accessdate=2020-07-18|work=中國報 China Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817152827/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20200714/%E2%97%A42018%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%BB%E5%AE%A1%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%B8%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%973%E2%97%A23%E5%B9%B489%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%81-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%9B%E8%AD%A6%E8%88%B9-%E4%BE%B5%E4%B8%9C/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

